
Ranger Help for: desert
=======================

SUMMARY:    
The desert terrain is a harsh terrain, hot and dry. Sand is the most
common feature in a desert area, it gets into everything. Life still
holds its own, but is far less abundant than some of the more hospitable
terrains such as forest. The Ranger population is fairly small in the
desert, for a lot of a Ranger's skills will not work there. Deserts
are most prominently known for being in Souvrael, but there others
around the realms.

=============================================================================
SEE ALSO: Individual terrains

